title: Carbs and Ratings
description: The project focuses on analyzing the relationship between the amount of carbohydrates in a recipe and the rating of the recipe.

title: Expository Visualization of Food
description: The project focuses on creating a graph to showcase a trend in processing levels in food bought at grocery stores.

title: Persuasive and Deceptive Visualization of Populations
description: This project focuses on creating a graph showcasing youth populations growth and decline.
